{"id":213999,"type":1,"name":"亜獣譚","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/f2/28/213999_AO9pK.jpg","summary":"　　愛と血に飢えた獣達の物語が今、始まる——\r\n　　人が異形の獣と化す病、害獣病が蔓延する世界。性格に難ありな害獣駆除兵のアキミア・ツキヒコは害獣を追って入った森の中で衛生兵の美女、ホシ・ソウと出会う。行方不明の弟を捜しているというソウに対し、アキミアは驚くべき提案をもちかける。その提案とは——『弟を助けてほしければ私と結婚して下さい』という、あまりにも不条理なモノだった。\r\n　　人と獣の魂の慟哭を描く異色ダークファンタジー、開幕。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>亚兽谭</li><li><span>册数: </span>8</li><li><span>话数: </span>73</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/20695\">江野スミ</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/6749\">小学館</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/22488\">マンガワン</a>、<a href=\"/person/9783\">裏サンデー</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>A JYU TAN</li><li><span>开始: </span>2016-12-11</li><li><span>结束: </span>2020-02-09</li><li><span>备注: </span>裏サンデー在2016年12月18日~2020年2月16日同步连载本作。</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":1,"on_hold":1},"tags":[{"name":"マンガ","count":2},{"name":"全8卷","count":1},{"name":"已完结","count":1},{"name":"漫画系列","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":20695,"image":"","name":"江野スミ","desc":"作者"},{"id":6749,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2c/ec/6749_prsn_O9b2I.jpg","name":"小学馆","desc":"出版社"},{"id":9783,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/03/5c/9783_prsn_RyZ9U.jpg","name":"里Sunday","desc":"连载杂志"},{"id":22488,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/01/7f/22488_prsn_BBZAP.jpg","name":"MangaONE","desc":"连载杂志"}],"comic":[{"id":214000,"name":"亜獣譚 (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/35/db/214000_vwu33.jpg"},{"id":256747,"name":"亜獣譚 (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/05/07/256747_dCCbZ.jpg"},{"id":256748,"name":"亜獣譚 (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/77/cd/256748_t6ryE.jpg"},{"id":256749,"name":"亜獣譚 (4)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/d0/39/256749_PnKjY.jpg"},{"id":272179,"name":"亜獣譚 (5)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/25/bd/272179_wzyI3.jpg"},{"id":303996,"name":"亜獣譚 (6)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/f6/2d/303996_r4613.jpg"},{"id":303997,"name":"亜獣譚 (7)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/1f/35/303997_dRO3R.jpg"},{"id":303998,"name":"亜獣譚 (8